Definition.WordDefinition:
papers \pa"pers\ n. pl. Documents providing information, esp. of an official nature about a person, vehicle, business, etc. See {paper}[9], n.
Syn: document, written document. [WordNet 1.5]
papers n : writing that provides information (especially information of an official nature) [syn: {document}, {written document}]
